You have shown me what true love feels like, and I am forever grateful for that. With every thought, every action, and every word, you have proven time and time again that you are my soulmate and my perfect match.

I know that I am not perfect, but with you by my side, I feel like anything is possible. You inspire me to be a better person, to reach for the stars, and to never give up on my dreams.

